        "Description": [
          {
            "text": "Our A4 Multifunctional Business Contract Office Document Folder is the ultimate organizational solution for professionals, students, and businesses. Crafted from high-quality, durable polyurethane (PU), this folder combines functionality with a sleek, professional design, making it ideal for corporate settings, travel, and everyday office use. Perfect for storing standard 8.5 x 11 letter-sized documents, contracts, reports, resumes, and presentations, it features practical pockets to keep papers secure and easily accessible. The portable and lightweight design ensures easy transportation, whether for meetings, school, or on-the-go document management. Customizable with your logo or branding, it’s a versatile promotional item for corporate events, anniversaries, or collegiate programs, supporting sustainable organizational habits. Sturdy construction resists wear and tear, protecting your important documents from damage. Suitable for filing cabinets, desk organization, or as a presentation portfolio, this folder is a must-have tool for staying efficient and professional in any environment.",
